{"tid":1512672,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺有班人郁啲就話人發國難財?","createTime":"2019-08-28T03:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T04:11:48.000Z","uid":71004,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb62b93b32b12aa7b64cba3530ff81ab90a7d66","tid":1512672,"uid":71004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:38:09.000Z","msg":"總覺得有班人專係上綱上線, 郁啲話人發國難財　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n透過標籤黎制造分化, 遏止反送中商品的出現, 防範思想散播同阻礙士氣　<br />\n<br />\n反送中必須有商品出現, 而且<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">百花齊放</span></strong>, 原因如下:<br />\n<br />\n1. <strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">製造更多抗爭下既得利益者</span></span></strong>：抗爭係要招攬更多人支持, 商家發現支持抗爭係有利可圖既, 自然會支持; 正如班既得利益者支持老共同政府一樣, 天下攘攘，皆為利往。<span style=\"color: red;\">天下熙熙，皆為利來</span>。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>文宣作用</strong></span>：意識形態實體化, 將抗爭思想變成本土文化同潮流, 以有助對外國 及 本地既宣傳<br />\n<br />\n3. 平反少數派既標籤, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反映民意, 凝聚士氣</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔覺"},{"pid":"44be271808a4de1a9d587f3cec17e5fb3e4254c2","tid":1512672,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:38:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=42664231\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ02F